 a true and complete copy of a resolution adopted by the Council of the City of New York on this 30th day of June, 2026 on file in this office.\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\nowidctlpar\\par\n\\tab\\tab\\tab\\tab\\par\n\\tab\\tab\\ul\\b                                                                \\ulnone\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\qj\\tqc\\tx4320\\tqc\\tx5040\\tqc\\tx5760\\b0                                            _____________________________\\par\n\\tab\\b Clerk of the Council of The City \\tab\\tab\\tab\\tab\\tab of New York\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\par\n}\n",
